---
const today = new Date();
---

<footer class="relative w-full z-50 flex flex-col items-start gap-5 bg-clrWhite">
	<div class="w-full px-5 mt-32">
		<section class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center justify-end md:justify-center w-full h-56 md:h-64 rounded-2xl bg-secondaryNeutral">

			<section class="relative flex w-full px-5 md:order-last">
				<div class="flex w-4/5 flex-col p-3 pr-6 md:p-6 md:pr-12 bg-primaryNeutral rounded-lg">
					<p class="text-base md:text-xl text-clrWhite">Vous souhaitez me faire passer un message ou voir mes travaux sur mes réseaux sociaux ?</p>
					<p class="text-base md:text-xl text-clrWhite">N’hésitez-pas !</p>
				</div>
				<div class="absolute w-fit right-5 bottom-0">
					<img class="w-20 md:w-36 h-auto" src="src/assets/chibi_moe.svg" alt="Personnage">
				</div>
			</section>
			

			<section class="flex flex-col justify-end h-full px-8 py-9 gap-2 md:justify-center md:gap-8 md:w-3/4">
				<p class="text-clrWhite md:text-3xl">On se contacte ?</p>
				<div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
					<a class="text-base text-clrWhite hover:underline" href="mailto:carolane.noel@outlook.com">carolane.noel@outlook.com</a>
					<ul class="flex gap-8">
						<li><a class="flex w-full px-1.5" href="https://www.behance.net/carolanenoel1"><img src="src/assets/logo_behance.svg" alt="Logo Behance"/></a></li>
						<li><a class="w-full px-1.5" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/carolane-noel-062000265/"><img src="src/assets/logo_linkedin.svg" alt="Logo LinkedIn"/></a></li>
						<li><a class="w-full px-1.5" href="https://www.instagram.com/ti.ra_mizu/"><img src="src/assets/logo_instagram.svg" alt="Logo Instagram"></a></li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</section>
			
		</section>
	</div>
	
	<section class="relative w-full">
		<img src="src/assets/footer-illu.png" alt="Illustration footer">
		<div class="absolute w-full bottom-2 text-base text-center text-clrWhite">
			&copy; {today.getFullYear()} Carolane. Tous droits réservés.
		</div>
	</section>
	
</footer>
